txt.en: You have been tasked with defeating the half-orc forces gathered at the entrances to the mines of Writhenset.
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Radhril for your reward!

'Would you accompany me on a mission, [placeholder]?

'The Free Peoples in the Wildwood have reported that the mines of Writhenset have been taken over by a group of half-orcs. It would seem they have the entrances to the mines completely guarded.

'If the mines of Writhenset are to ever again be safe, this group of half-orcs must be removed.'
Complete Mission: Invaders on the Delf
The entrances to the mines of Writhenset have been seized by half-orc intruders!\n\nYour mission is to defeat the half-orc forces gathered at the entrances to the mines of Writhenset.
Some monsters in this mission will attempt to lay down traps that will give you a debuff if caught in the trap.
Your mission is to defeat the half-orc forces gathered at the entrances to the mines of Writhenset.\n\nSpeak to Radhril.
'We have done well, [placeholder]. With the half-orc mining operation defeated, the mines of Writhenset will soon enough be safe. I am sure the Free Peoples are thankful for our efforts.'
